SUMMARY:
Lower aspirate_speed, higher dispense_speed, and longer dispense_wait_time seem to correlate with lower deviation and variability. The best performing experiment used these parameters effectively. The recommendations seek to further optimize these parameters while exploring the limits of the parameter ranges.
